{"tid":423911,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺中文真係一樣好神奇既文字","createTime":"2017-10-04T09:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T14:18:03.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c81e9fdad064bdbe4f43e12b89b023690fcc7d16","tid":423911,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"中文有啲字我地唔需要特別認字我地都會讀，例如係細個無人教過你，你幼稚園時已經認到簡單生字，到小學就算見過一啲未見過又唔算深既詞語都會自動識讀<br />\n<br />\n但相反其他文字你最多識得佢啲文法，但要靈活運用既話一定要不斷學識啲vocab至得，唔係既話你淨係渣住啲字母，其餘乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b28d2b49de13a1f4377df1ea42b6a547fba2768","tid":423911,"uid":114537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:05:29.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦Ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c4e75e310ead17a8cdb7d67a8099ef2754696c","tid":423911,"uid":114537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"自動識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4cf4fb92f4228c615de53df88708caaaed9898","tid":423911,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自動識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎,我記得以前啲課文係自己睇完識讀"},{"pid":"3d2d7e90a4bfd756bda96adbf6c6c4650537ee74","tid":423911,"uid":21310,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15f356515c12404dab15c4fc03f08cc854029ddb","tid":423911,"uid":35418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自動識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎,我記得以前啲課文係自己睇完識讀</blockquote><br />\n因為有人教你, 有邊讀邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdaf8cdae704858426c14b3697b005950a790642","tid":423911,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自動識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎,我記得以前啲課文係自己睇完識讀</blockquote><br />\n弊在錯呢<br />\n骨骼 怦然 劉備 風靡 渲染 紈絝子弟 緋聞 中國"},{"pid":"f128b0c79c0c3302029ddf99a3d8eb77811ca3e5","tid":423911,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自動識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎,我記得以前啲課文係自己睇完識讀</blockquote><br />\n弊在錯呢<br />\n骨骼 怦然 劉備 風靡 渲染 紈絝子弟 緋聞 中國</blockquote><br />\n小學喎,我當小一,你講呢啲我當骨骼,緋聞同中國課文會有,其餘果啲要自動學識唔駛係好細個未有啦"},{"pid":"99e68ac06342533192e4a0a9fbd5363a6d81fa7f","tid":423911,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"即係你地學中文係要老師教過隻字,例如係一至十我你他她它果啲,你地至會識?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb15672c4fae267e49953df73dfd57a914bbac1","tid":423911,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"英文世界第一"},{"pid":"a0f5b4bbd765b5147b760314c97b4ad182ae2aad","tid":423911,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:41:11.000Z","msg":"自修生話比你知其實唔係！有好多野好簡單，一講你就明，但係無人講過，你要去理解其實好難，越簡單既越難？好多人以為自己讀書成績好係因為自己勤力，其實你冇同一個完全靠自學既人比較！同一篇文，有人讀比你聽同你自己睇要做到相同既認知，係差成倍時間，尤其是語言！<br />\n<br />\n不過，中文某方面的確係容易學過英文，因為兩個原因，中文既常用字詞冇英文咁多，你認到一千個字以經可以基本應用，英文你要記一萬個！點解中字記小字d？因為佢無論詞語/文化/句子都好講推理/理解上文下理。你越聰明學中文就越快，英文呢？你記性越好就越快。<br />\n<br />\n普遍現代人都越來越聰明，但係認憶力好既人一樣要花大量死記既時間，個過程一定好痛苦，不過好處係唔洗太多思考！"},{"pid":"947d62f944373c7d96b5c96cf70ed68bfdf789f4","tid":423911,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"因為你睇電視聽過咪識讀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到英文唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實中文同好需要記性 只係詞庫較小<br />\n但英文你學左拼音咪一樣識讀 中文反而拼唔到"},{"pid":"e00e6261c79595de017ea3858efa4602f1f815be","tid":423911,"uid":74207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孟加拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMangala Effect"},{"pid":"227566b1038446b55217bfd537689da1e7e069d8","tid":423911,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你睇電視聽過咪識讀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到英文唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實中文同樣好需要記性 只係詞庫較小<br />\n英文你學左拼音咪一樣識讀 中文反而拼唔到 唔記得就讀唔到隻字<br />\n利申 識人唔識讀啲常用字 但正常交流都識講</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f9157b876f75dba301f9d0eee5535e8df3a8c260","tid":423911,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:34:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你睇電視聽過咪識讀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到英文唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實中文同好需要記性 只係詞庫較小<br />\n但英文你學左拼音咪一樣識讀 中文反而拼唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一段同意<br />\n第二段有保留 比起好多歐洲語言嘅拼寫法<br />\n英文嘅拼寫係冇咁可靠"},{"pid":"1fa3a28ed00735955a85be6dee783e7876f9565b","tid":423911,"uid":32753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自動識讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎,我記得以前啲課文係自己睇完識讀</blockquote><br />\n弊在錯呢<br />\n骨骼 怦然 劉備 風靡 渲染 紈絝子弟 緋聞 中國</blockquote><br />\n淨係唔識中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係我真心左"},{"pid":"98d9b13bbf0091801c97bc0823e3c331569d280c","tid":423911,"uid":114294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係你地學中文係要老師教過隻字,例如係一至十我你他她它果啲,你地至會識?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪咁自大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔教點識呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a383854a31173fd8693cfac2f2af7ef41133ca7","tid":423911,"uid":124899,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"踩低自己語言抬高人地語言係港狗心理變態之處，樓主無謂對牛彈琴"},{"pid":"42927aa613e32ce6fd4779a5a9f4dd3dbea437ed","tid":423911,"uid":116000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇認識過英文"},{"pid":"99f3d7672c04360a58b42a7b90479d25d2467f3c","tid":423911,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為你睇電視聽過咪識讀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到英文唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實中文同好需要記性 只係詞庫較小<br />\n但英文你學左拼音咪一樣識讀 中文反而拼唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一段同意<br />\n第二段有保留 比起好多歐洲語言嘅拼寫法<br />\n英文嘅拼寫係冇咁可靠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求其舉幾個例:<br />\n<br />\nough: though, through, rough <br />\nea: head, mead, tread, seat, dead, meat, great<br />\now: cow, low, sow, row"},{"pid":"5f445b5c4867cd507d642c0d18d80c2dd1070721","tid":423911,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為你睇電視聽過咪識讀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到英文唔係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實中文同好需要記性 只係詞庫較小<br />\n但英文你學左拼音咪一樣識讀 中文反而拼唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一段同意<br />\n第二段有保留 比起好多歐洲語言嘅拼寫法<br />\n英文嘅拼寫係冇咁可靠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求其舉幾個例:<br />\n<br />\nough: though, through, rough <br />\nea: head, mead, tread, seat, dead, meat, great<br />\now: cow, low, sow, row</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nenterprise,  entrepreneur 同字不同音<br />\nlead (帶領)  lead (鉛)  同字不同音不同意<br />\nto/two/too 同音不同字不同意<br />\n<br />\n不過樓主主要係講<br />\n<br />\n牛，公牛，母牛<br />\nbulls cows cattle<br />\n<br />\n前者舉一反三<br />\n後者毫無關係<br />\n<br />\n中文大部份係上面<br />\n當然英文都有所謂prefix suffix, 但明顯可重用程度不能同日而語<br />\n<br />\n不過可能現代人愛虛榮同比較自私<br />\n講野對方聽唔明睇唔明反而覺得自己專業<br />\n隔行如隔山既英文反而比到虛榮依類人<br />\n依類人亦無視英文接近無限生詞依個缺點<br />\n<br />\n你睇下，一個膠盒，可以係個牌子名<br />\n收費處係個姓<br />\n<br />\n就知依類語言成詞係唔講邏輯，只講習慣"},{"pid":"f8fb03c0e4acfeb71150ecb4c9b447403577bfac","tid":423911,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"複製一段<br />\n人地英文人反而會反思下，香港人就只識讚英文<br />\n其實「英文」「易學」早就比「政治正確」更恐怖<br />\n<br />\nThe bandage was wound around the wound.<br />\nThe farm was used to produce produce.<br />\nThe dump was so full that it had to refuse more refuse.<br />\nWe must polish the Polish furniture.<br />\nHe could lead if he would get the lead out.<br />\nThe soldier decided to desert his dessert in the desert.<br />\nSince there is no time like the present, he thought it was time to present the present.<br />\nA bass was painted on the head of the bass drum.<br />\nWhen shot at, the dove dove into the bushes.<br />\nI did not object to the object.<br />\nThe insurance was invalid for the invalid.<br />\nThere was a row among the oarsmen about how to row.<br />\nThey were too close to the door to close it.<br />\nThe buck does funny things when the does are present.<br />\nA seamstress and a sewer fell down into a sewer line.<br />\nTo help with planting, the farmer taught his sow to sow.<br />\nThe wind was too strong to wind the sail.<br />\nUpon seeing the tear in the painting I shed a tear.<br />\nI had to subject the subject to a series of tests.<br />\nHow can I intimate this to my most intimate friend?"},{"pid":"d0db28c374df9d5f57fb014b098bce3000617dee","tid":423911,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:55:55.000Z","msg":"不過崇英文撚又會話英文多變靈活係咪﹖<br />\n明白既。<br />\n英文係神聖不可侵犯的。"},{"pid":"15c6a374d10181a916e7cb8293cd5212b24a141b","tid":423911,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"有條鬼佬咁講&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nGood stuff. It's only the tip of the iceberg, English has a massive amount of words with double meanings, then there is similar sounding words that are spelt differently.<br />\nI never realised how bad it was until I started learning Chinese and teaching other people English.<br />\n<br />\n哈哈，同高登仔講反調。"},{"pid":"79946509b19e70149b9794900f107acb0df55cb1","tid":423911,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"英文重要用大量拉丁字黎用響法律之上去定義詞意。<br />\n言而崇英文者會話「英文好準確」<br />\n<br />\n是事係，英文好唔準確，要借用拉丁字詞黎增加準確度。"}]}